  "decision_conditions": [
    "<p>The Development hereby permitted shall only be carried out and completed strictly in accordance with the submitted plans hereby approved and any subsequent approval of details.\r\n</p><p><br></p><p>\r\nREASON: To ensure that the development hereby permitted is carried out in full accordance with the plans hereby approved.\r\n</p>",
    "<p>The development hereby permitted must be begun not later than the expiration of three years beginning with the date of this permission.</p><p><br></p><p>\r\n</p><p>\r\nREASON: In order to comply with the provisions of the Town and Country Planning Act 1990 (as amended).</p><p>\r\n</p>",
    "&lt;p&gt;The development hereby approved shall be operated in full compliance with the noise levels outlined in the submitted noise report, ensuring that the rating level of noise emissions from the air source heat pump does not exceed 5dB below the background noise level when assessed in accordance with BS4142:2014+A1:2019.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Should any changes to the approved plant or equipment occur, a new noise assessment must be submitted to and approved in writing by the Local Planning Authority to demonstrate continued compliance with BS4142:2014+A1:2019.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;REASON: To safeguard the amenity of neighbouring occupiers and ensure compliance with Policy LP2 of Hackney’s Local Plan and the London Plan’s strategic noise policies.&lt;/p&gt;"
